NAME
    File::Rotate::Backup - Make backups of multiple directories and rotate
    them

SYNOPSIS
    my $backup = File::Rotate::Backup->new({ archive_copies => 2, dir_copies
    => 1, backup_dir => '/backups', file_prefix => 'backup_' });

    $backup->backup([ [ '/etc/httpd/conf' => 'httpd_conf' ], [ '/var/named'
    => 'named' ], ]);

    $backup->rotate;

DESCRIPTION
    This module will make backups and rotate according to your
    specification.

